messageBody:
Chandrasekar Ramakrishnan wrote:

> On behalf of the new comers of the group, I'll be pleased if the members
> can share the tutorials on Junit and eclipse. Any links or websites can
> even help to have a start.

Yes, but you should really search the web, since that's what the web is for.

I highly recommend these for JUnit (use Google and site:xxx if you can't
find the article on each site)

* http://www.diasparsoftware.com - Articles/Presentations - JUnit: A
Starter Guide
* http://www.clarkware.com - the JUnit Primer

For Eclipse and for JUnit-with-Eclipse, I'll let others provide their links.
